      "content": "function nthFibonacci(n){\n\n    // base case\n    if (n <= 1) {\n        return n;\n    }\n    \n    // sum of the two preceding \n    // Fibonacci numbers\n    return nthFibonacci(n - 1) + nthFibonacci(n - 2);\n}\n\nlet n = 5;\nlet result = nthFibonacci(n);\nconsole.log(result);",
